WHERE BAN_ESTADO_EJECUCION = 'EJECUTANDO' AND DATE_TRUNC('HOUR',FECHA_PROCESO) < DATE_TRUNC('HOUR',CURRENT_TIMESTAMP) AND DES_PROCESO = '#PRY_DWH.V_0772_CTL_SESION_NOMBRE'

INSERT INTO <?=odiRef.getObjectName("INH_SEG_CNTL_FECHAS_UPD") ?> (COD_SESION, DES_PROCESO, FECHA_INICIAL, FECHA_FINAL, FECHA_PROCESO, BAN_ESTADO_EJECUCION, DES_ESTADO_EJECUCION, BAN_PERIODICIDAD) ( SELECT #PRY_DWH.V_0772_CTL_SESION COD_SESION, '#PRY_DWH.V_0772_CTL_SESION_NOMBRE' DES_PROCESO, NVL(T2.FECHA_FINAL,DATE_TRUNC('DAY',CURRENT_TIMESTAMP)) FECHA_INICIAL, DATE_TRUNC('HOUR',CURRENT_TIMESTAMP) FECHA_FINAL, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP FECHA_PROCESO, 'EJECUTANDO' BAN_ESTADO_EJECUCION, NULL DES_ESTADO_EJECUCION, NVL(T2.BAN_PERIODICIDAD,'D') BAN_PERIODICIDAD FROM (SELECT 0 COD_DUMMY) T1 -- SE UTILIZA COMO PRIMERA TABLA EN CASO DE QUE LA SIGUIENTE CONSULTA NO ARROJE RESULTADOS LEFT JOIN (SELECT 0 COD_DUMMY, *, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY DES_PROCESO ORDER BY FECHA_INICIAL DESC, FECHA_FINAL DESC) FLAG FROM <?=odiRef.getObjectName("INH_SEG_CNTL_FECHAS_UPD") ?> WHERE BAN_ESTADO_EJECUCION ='FINALIZADO') T2 ON (T1.COD_DUMMY = T2.COD_DUMMY AND T2.FLAG = 1 AND T2.DES_PROCESO = '#PRY_DWH.V_0772_CTL_SESION_NOMBRE') )

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS <?=odiRef.getObjectName("INH_SEG_CNTL_FECHAS_UPD") ?> ( COD_SESION BIGINT, DES_PROCESO CHARACTER VARYING(100), FECHA_INICIAL TIMESTAMP, FECHA_FINAL TIMESTAMP, FECHA_PROCESO TIMESTAMP, BAN_ESTADO_EJECUCION CHARACTER VARYING(12), DES_ESTADO_EJECUCION CHARACTER VARYING(250), BAN_PERIODICIDAD CHARACTER VARYING(2) ) DISTRIBUTE ON RANDOM

SELECT CASE WHEN T1.BAN_PYME = 1 THEN ', A.BAN_PYME FROM <?=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_CATALOG") ?>.<?=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_SCHEMA") ?>.TBL_TMP_CLIEN_EXT_TMSP_PREP A' WHEN T1.BAN_PYME = 2 THEN ', CASE WHEN B.COD_PLAN_ACTUAL IS NOT NULL THEN ''S'' ELSE ''N'' END AS BAN_PYME FROM <?=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_CATALOG") ?>.<?=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_SCHEMA") ?>.TBL_TMP_CLIEN_EXT_TMSP_PREP A LEFT JOIN #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_DB_DWH_AEXTERNAS.#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_GAMERCADOS.TBL_PLANES_PYME_R5 B ON (A.COD_PLAN = B.COD_PLAN_ACTUAL)' WHEN T1.BAN_PYME = 3 THEN ', COALESCE ( CASE WHEN B.COD_PLAN_ACTUAL IS NOT NULL THEN ''S'' ELSE NULL END, A.BAN_PYME, ''N'') AS BAN_PYME FROM <?=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_CATALOG") ?>.<?=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_SCHEMA") ?>.TBL_TMP_CLIEN_EXT_TMSP_PREP A LEFT JOIN #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_DB_DWH_AEXTERNAS.#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_GAMERCADOS.TBL_PLANES_PYME_R5 B ON (A.COD_PLAN = B.COD_PLAN_ACTUAL)' WHEN T1.BAN_PYME = 4 THEN ', CASE WHEN A.BAN_PYME=''S'' THEN ''S'' WHEN B.COD_PLAN_ACTUAL IS NOT NULL THEN ''S'' ELSE ''N'' END AS BAN_PYME FROM <?=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_CATALOG") ?>.<?=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_SCHEMA") ?>.TBL_TMP_CLIEN_EXT_TMSP_PREP A LEFT JOIN #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_DB_DWH_AEXTERNAS.#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_GAMERCADOS.TBL_PLANES_PYME_R5 B ON (A.COD_PLAN = B.COD_PLAN_ACTUAL)' END BAN_PYME FROM (SELECT #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_BAN_PYME AS BAN_PYME) T1

, PRODUCTO , FECHA_INGRESO , CLASE_PLAN , SEGM_CFM , FLAG_PRIM_EVENTO , FLAG_PRIM_CARGA , CATEGORIA_PREPAGO , GRP_SERVICIO , FLAG_SEG_CARGA , FLAG_ACT_MANUAL , FLAG_CLASE_ESP_ESCALERA , FLAG_ELEG5MIN , FLAG_VOLUMEN_ELEG , GRUPO_PRODUCTO , FLAG_PLANCONELEG , CATEGORIA_ESCALERA , CATEGORIA_PRESUPUESTO , PLANTYPEID , PLANTYPEID_DESC , PRODUCTO_GAI , ESPECIAL_GAI , DOLARES_GAI , MIN_INC_C_F_O , MIN_INC_C , MIN_INC_F , MIN_INC_O , TIPO_BOLSA , GRUPO_AUX1 , TIPO_PLAN_MINACTIVO , MICROCELDA , CATE_PLAN_MINACTIVO , CALL_TICKET_CONF_ALL , CONFIRMATION_TICKET_ALL_WB , CONFIDENC_SERVICIOS_DATOS_ALL , UPD_LLS_A_OTRO , TIPO_FACTURACION , TIPO_CONTROL_MAGUARE , TIPO_PLAN , VLR_CFM_VOZ , VLR_CFM_DATOS , VLR_CFM_DATOS_IMP , CANT_MIN_INC_ELEG_TD , CANT_SMS_CLARO_INC , CANT_MB_INC_PLAN , CANT_MB_BB_INC_PLAN , SEGMENTO_PLAN , NAVEGACION_PLAN , VLR_MIN_INC_CLARO , VLR_MIN_INC_FIJOS , VLR_MIN_INC_OTROS , VAL_MIN_ADIC_CLARO , VAL_MIN_ADIC_FIJOS , VAL_MIN_ADIC_OTROS , VAL_SMS_ADIC_CLARO , VAL_CANT_ELEG_FIJOS , VAL_CANT_ELEG_ONNET , VAL_CANT_ELEG_OFFNET , CANT_ELEG_TD , NOMBRE_CUOTA_PCRF , TIPO_NAVEGACION_PCRF , TIPO_PLAN_PCRF , ROUTING_CATEGORY_BCSC , NVL(TECNOLOGIA,'Sin Tecnologia') AS TECNOLOGIA , NVL(FAMILIA_PLAN,'Sin Familia Plan') AS FAMILIA_PLAN , NVL(CATEGORIA_PLAN,'Sin Categoria Asignada') AS CATEGORIA_PLAN , NVL(INDICADOR_PLAN,'Sin Indicador') AS INDICADOR_PLAN , NVL(BAN_REVENTA,'N') AS BAN_REVENTA , NVL(BAN_PYME,'N') AS BAN_PYME , NVL(TIPO_OFERTA,'Na') AS TIPO_OFERTA , NVL(BAN_CONVERTIBLE_LDI,'N') AS BAN_CONVERTIBLE_LDI , NVL(PSB_MINU_CONV_LDI,0) AS PSB_MINU_CONV_LDI , NVL(PSB_VALOR_CONV_LDI,0) AS PSB_VALOR_CONV_LDI , NVL(PSB_VALOR_CONV_PREFERE_LDI,0) AS PSB_VALOR_CONV_PREFERE_LDI , NVL(PSB_MINU_CONV_ZONA_LDI,0) AS PSB_MINU_CONV_ZONA_LDI , NVL(PSB_VALOR_CONV_ZONA_LDI,0) AS PSB_VALOR_CONV_ZONA_LDI , NVL(PSB_MINU_CONV_PREFERE_LDI,0) AS PSB_MINU_CONV_PREFERE_LDI , VAL_IVA_SERV_VOZ , VAL_IVA_SERV_DATOS , VAL_IVA_SERV_DATOS_IMP , VAL_IVA_SMS , BAN_PLAN_MEGASIM , VAL_RECARGA_INI_MEGASIM , NVL(BAN_PLAN_SIM_UNICA,0) AS BAN_PLAN_SIM_UNICA , CANT_MIN_INC_LDI_1 , CANT_MIN_INC_LDI_2 , CANT_MIN_INC_LDI_RM , VAL_ADIC_KB , COD_PASE , DES_CONSU_ADI_DATOS , COD_PERIODO_TIEMPO
FROM <?=odiRef.getInfo("SRC_CATALOG") ?>.<?=odiRef.getInfo("SRC_SCHEMA") ?>.TBL_DIM_PLANES_T2 WHERE MC_ACTUA = '1'

SELECT /*+PARALLEL(#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_PARALLEL)*/ A.TMCODE||'-'||A.SPCODE COD_PLAN, A.TMCODE, A.SPCODE, CASE WHEN (A.SNCODE=3013) THEN (B.VLR_CFM) ELSE (A.ACCESSFEE) END VLR_CFM, A.ACCGLCODE, A.USGGLCODE, A.VSCODE, A.VSDATE FROM #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_SYSADM.MPULKTMB A LEFT JOIN ( SELECT /*+PARALLEL(#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_PARALLEL)*/ TMCODE, SPCODE, VSCODE, SUM(ACCESSFEE) VLR_CFM FROM #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_SYSADM.MPULKTMB WHERE SNCODE IN (3013,11538,11537) GROUP BY TMCODE, SPCODE, VSCODE ) B ON (A.TMCODE = B.TMCODE AND A.SPCODE = B.SPCODE AND A.VSCODE = B.VSCODE) WHERE A.SNCODE IN (3013,3)

SELECT /*+PARALLEL(#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_PARALLEL)*/ TMCODE, INITCAP(REPLACE(DES,CHR(10),'')) PLAN_DESC, VSDATE FROM #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_SYSADM.MPUTMTAB WHERE VSCODE = (SELECT MAX(VSCODE) FROM #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_SYSADM.MPUTMTAB TM WHERE MPUTMTAB.TMCODE = TM.TMCODE) AND STATUS='P'

SELECT /*+PARALLEL(#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_PARALLEL)*/ DISTINCT TMCODE||'-'||SPCODE AS COD_PLAN , DECODE(PREPAGO,0,'Prepago','Postpago') AS PRODUCTO , DECODE(PREPAGO,3,'DATOS','VOZ') AS GRP_SERVICIO , CASE WHEN PREPAGO IN (1,4,5) THEN '2' WHEN PREPAGO IN (2) THEN '1' WHEN PREPAGO IN (3) THEN '3' ELSE '9' END PLANTYPEID , CASE WHEN PREPAGO IN (1,4,5) THEN 'Cerrado' WHEN PREPAGO IN (2) THEN 'Abierto' WHEN PREPAGO IN (3) THEN 'Datos' ELSE 'Otro' END PLANTYPEID_DESC , PREPAGO AS TIPO_PLAN_MINACTIVO , MICROCELDA , CATE_PLAN AS CATE_PLAN_MINACTIVO , CASE WHEN UPPER(SUBSTR(CLASE_PLAN,INSTR(CLASE_PLAN,',',1,4)+1,(INSTR(CLASE_PLAN,',',1,5)-INSTR(CLASE_PLAN,',',1,4))-1))='PYMES' THEN 'S' ELSE 'N' END BAN_PYME FROM #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_SYSADM.INH_TMSP_PREP

SELECT /*+PARALLEL(#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_PARALLEL)*/ TMCODE, CASE WHEN EQUIVALENCIA = 1 THEN 'S' ELSE NULL END BAN_REVENTA, CASE WHEN EQUIVALENCIA = 2 THEN DESARROLLO ELSE NULL END INDICADOR_PLAN, CASE WHEN EQUIVALENCIA = 1 THEN 'REVENTA' ELSE 'INDICADOR' END REVENTA_INDICADOR FROM sysadm.INH_CONFIG_PLANES WHERE EQUIVALENCIA IN (1,2)

CREATE TEMPORARY TABLE TBL_TMP_CLIEN_MPULKTMB AS ( SELECT T1.COD_PLAN , T1.TMCODE , T1.SPCODE , T1.VLR_CFM , T1.ACCGLCODE , T1.USGGLCODE , CURRENT_TIMESTAMP FECHA_INGRESO , 0 SEGM_CFM FROM db_dwh_stage.clientes.TBL_TMP_CLIEN_EXT_MPULKTMB T1 WHERE T1.VSCODE = ( SELECT MAX(VSCODE) FROM db_dwh_stage.clientes.TBL_TMP_CLIEN_EXT_MPULKTMB IXM WHERE T1.COD_PLAN = IXM.COD_PLAN ) ORDER BY 2 ASC ) DISTRIBUTE ON (COD_PLAN)

UPDATE <?=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_CLIEN_PLANES") ?> T1 SET TMCODE = NVL(T2.TMCODE,'-1'), SPCODE = NVL(T2.SPCODE,'-1'), VLR_CFM = NVL(T2.VLR_CFM,0), ACCGLCODE = NVL(T2.ACCGLCODE,'Sin Código'), USGGLCODE = NVL(T2.USGGLCODE,'Sin Código'), FECHA_INGRESO = NVL(T2.FECHA_INGRESO,'1900-01-01 00:00:00'), SEGM_CFM = NVL(T2.SEGM_CFM,0) FROM TBL_TMP_CLIEN_MPULKTMB T2 WHERE (T1.COD_PLAN = T2.COD_PLAN)

INSERT INTO <?=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_CLIEN_PLANES") ?> (COD_PLAN, TMCODE, SPCODE, VLR_CFM, ACCGLCODE, USGGLCODE, PRODUCTO, FECHA_INGRESO, SEGM_CFM) SELECT T2.COD_PLAN , NVL(T2.TMCODE,'-1') , NVL(T2.SPCODE,'-1') , NVL(T2.VLR_CFM,0) , NVL(T2.ACCGLCODE,'Sin Código') , NVL(T2.USGGLCODE,'Sin Código') , 'Sin Producto' , NVL(T2.FECHA_INGRESO,'1900-01-01 00:00:00') , NVL(T2.SEGM_CFM,0) FROM TBL_TMP_CLIEN_MPULKTMB T2 LEFT OUTER JOIN <?=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_CLIEN_PLANES") ?> T1 ON (T1.COD_PLAN = T2.COD_PLAN) WHERE T1.COD_PLAN IS NULL

UPDATE <?=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_CLIEN_PLANES") ?> T1 SET PLAN_DESC = NVL(T2.PLAN_DESC,'Sin Plan CRM') FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT TMCODE, PLAN_DESC FROM <?=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_TMP_CLIEN_EXT_MPUTMTAB") ?> )T2 WHERE T1.TMCODE = NVL(T2.TMCODE,'-1')

UPDATE <?=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_CLIEN_PLANES") ?> T1 SET PAQUETE_DESC = NVL(T2.PAQUETE_DESC,'Sin Paquete de Descuento') FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT SPCODE, PAQUETE_DESC FROM <?=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_TMP_CLIEN_EXT_MPUSPTAB") ?> )T2 WHERE T1.SPCODE = NVL(T2.SPCODE,'-1')

CREATE TEMPORARY TABLE TBL_TMP_CLIEN_TMPSP_PREP AS ( SELECT COD_PLAN , GRP_SERVICIO , TIPO_PLAN_MINACTIVO , MICROCELDA , CATE_PLAN_MINACTIVO --LA FUENTE DE LA CONSULTA SE DEFINE DINÁMICAMENTE A PARTIR DE LA VARIABLE BAN_PYME #PRY_DWH.V_0772_CTL_BAN_PYME ) DISTRIBUTE ON (COD_PLAN)

UPDATE <?=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_CLIEN_PLANES") ?> T1 SET GRP_SERVICIO = NVL(T2.GRP_SERVICIO,'Sin Grupo'), TIPO_PLAN_MINACTIVO = NVL(T2.TIPO_PLAN_MINACTIVO,'-1'), MICROCELDA = NVL(T2.MICROCELDA,'Sin Microcelda'), CATE_PLAN_MINACTIVO = NVL(T2.CATE_PLAN_MINACTIVO,'Sin Plan'), BAN_PYME = NVL(T2.BAN_PYME,'N') FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT COD_PLAN,GRP_SERVICIO, TIPO_PLAN_MINACTIVO, MICROCELDA, CATE_PLAN_MINACTIVO, BAN_PYME FROM TBL_TMP_CLIEN_TMPSP_PREP) T2 WHERE (T1.COD_PLAN = T2.COD_PLAN)

INSERT INTO <?=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_CLIEN_PLANES") ?> (COD_PLAN, PRODUCTO, GRP_SERVICIO, TIPO_PLAN_MINACTIVO, MICROCELDA, CATE_PLAN_MINACTIVO, BAN_PYME) SELECT T2.COD_PLAN ,'Sin Producto' ,NVL(T2.GRP_SERVICIO,'Sin Grupo') ,NVL(T2.TIPO_PLAN_MINACTIVO,'-1') ,NVL(T2.MICROCELDA,'Sin Microcelda') ,NVL(T2.CATE_PLAN_MINACTIVO,'Sin Plan') ,NVL(T2.BAN_PYME,'N') FROM TBL_TMP_CLIEN_TMPSP_PREP T2 LEFT OUTER JOIN <?=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_CLIEN_PLANES") ?> T1 ON (T1.COD_PLAN = T2.COD_PLAN) WHERE T1.COD_PLAN IS NULL

CREATE TEMPORARY TABLE TBL_TMP_CLIEN_TMSP_PREP AS (SELECT COD_PLAN , PRODUCTO FROM db_dwh_stage.clientes.TBL_TMP_CLIEN_EXT_TMSP_PREP WHERE COD_PLAN IN (SELECT COD_PLAN FROM db_dwh_stage.clientes.TBL_CLIEN_PLANES WHERE PRODUCTO = 'Sin Producto') )

UPDATE <?=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_CLIEN_PLANES") ?> T1 SET PRODUCTO = NVL(T2.PRODUCTO,'Sin Producto') FROM TBL_TMP_CLIEN_TMSP_PREP T2 WHERE T1.COD_PLAN = T2.COD_PLAN AND T1.PRODUCTO <> NVL(T2.PRODUCTO,'Sin Producto')

UPDATE <?=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_CLIEN_PLANES") ?> SET SEGM_CFM = CASE WHEN VLR_CFM BETWEEN 0 AND 20000 THEN '1- 0 a 20 mil' WHEN VLR_CFM BETWEEN 20001 AND 40000 THEN '2- 20 a 40 mil' WHEN VLR_CFM BETWEEN 40001 AND 70000 THEN '3- 40 a 70 mil' WHEN VLR_CFM BETWEEN 70001 AND 90000 THEN '4- 70 a 90 mil' WHEN VLR_CFM BETWEEN 90001 AND 120000 THEN '5- 90 a 120 mil' WHEN VLR_CFM BETWEEN 120001 AND 180000 THEN '6- 120 a 180 mil' WHEN VLR_CFM BETWEEN 180001 AND 250000 THEN '7- 180 a 250 mil' WHEN VLR_CFM > 250000 THEN '8- 250 y mas...' END
SELECT /*+PARALLEL(#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_PARALLEL)*/ A.TMCODE, A.SPCODE, MAX(A.VERSION) AS VER FROM #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_SYSADM.INH_DETALLE_PLAN_PAQ A GROUP BY A.TMCODE, A.SPCODE

SELECT /*+PARALLEL(#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_PARALLEL)*/ D.TMCODE, D.SPCODE, D.TIPO_BOLSA, D.TIPO_CONTROL_MAGUARE, D.TIPO_PLAN, D.TIPO_MEDIDA, REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(D.DESCRIPCION,CHR(10),''),CHR(8),''),CHR(9),'') AS PLAN_DESC_COMPLETA, D.VERSION, CASE WHEN UPPER(D.TIPO_PLAN) = 'VOZ' THEN NVL(D.CFM_VOZ,0) + NVL(D.CFM_DATOS,0) + NVL(D.CFM_DATOS_IMP,0) WHEN UPPER(D.TIPO_PLAN) = 'BUNDLE' THEN NVL(D.CFM_VOZ,0) ELSE 0 END AS VLR_CFM_VOZ, CASE WHEN UPPER(D.TIPO_PLAN) = 'DATOS' THEN NVL(D.CFM_VOZ,0) WHEN UPPER(D.TIPO_PLAN) = -- Actualizar CATEGORIA_PLAN UPDATE <?=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_DIM_PLANES_T2") ?> T1 SET CATEGORIA_PLAN = ( CASE WHEN (UPPER(T1.PRODUCTO) = 'POSTPAGO') THEN (CASE WHEN (T2.TECNOLOGIA = 'Blackberry') THEN 'BB' WHEN ((T2.FAMILIA_PLAN = 'Empresarial') AND (T2.Tipo_Plan = 'Voz')) THEN 'EMPRESARIAL' WHEN (T2.TECNOLOGIA = 'Internet movil') THEN 'INTERNET' WHEN (T2.TECNOLOGIA = 'Iphone') THEN 'IPHONE' WHEN ((T2.FAMILIA_PLAN = 'Masivo') AND (T2.Tipo_Plan = 'Voz')) THEN 'MASIVO' WHEN (T2.TECNOLOGIA = 'Smartphone') THEN 'OTROS SMARTPHONE' WHEN (T2.TECNOLOGIA = 'Transaccionales') THEN 'Transaccionales' WHEN (T2.TECNOLOGIA = 'IoT') THEN 'IoT' ELSE 'Sin Categoria Asignada' END) WHEN (UPPER(T1.PRODUCTO)='PREPAGO') THEN (CASE WHEN (T2.TECNOLOGIA = 'Sim Card') THEN 'CHIP CLARO' WHEN (T2.TECNOLOGIA = 'Kit') THEN 'KIT' WHEN (T2.TECNOLOGIA = 'Chip Costa') THEN 'WB EST CHIP COSTA' WHEN (T2.TECNOLOGIA = 'Estrategico') THEN 'WB ESTRATEGICO' WHEN (T2.TECNOLOGIA = 'Portabilidad') THEN 'WB POR SEGUNDOS' WHEN (T2.TECNOLOGIA = 'Tactico') THEN 'WB TACTICO' ELSE 'Sin Categoria Asignada' END) ELSE 'Sin Categoria Asignada' END) FROM TBL_TMP_CLIEN_DET_PLAN_FIN T2 WHERE T1.TMCODE = T2.TMCODE AND T1.SPCODE = T2.SPCODE AND T1.MC_ACTUA = '1'
